data.description: Experience modern elegance in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem located just 15 minutes from downtown. Step into this beautiful home, where you'll find a stunning kitchen with quartz countertops and soft-close drawers, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The lovely master bedroom awaits, complete with a tile shower in the ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet.Enjoy year-round comfort with central A/C and the added convenience of a central vacuum system. Unwind in your own private, fenced backyard, creating an ideal space for relaxation. Plus, you'll appreciate the proximity to local commerce. Make this dream home yours by scheduling an appointment today!
